                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <label>aboveThreshold</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <description>This auto-launched flow will take a projectId as input. 

If no ID is passed it will END.

If project doesn&apos;t meet required threshold.   It will END.
 
It will then grab the Sales Team AE, RVP, AVP, SE and SE Mgr from the project record AND grab the GNG committee from the GNG committee record then stage the data in the override request object for the justification.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
